# --- policy: repo-owned after init; update diffs, never replaces --------------
# (guard-secrets.sh is mechanism since v0.21.0, format.sh since v0.23.0:
# their policy is harness.conf data. The verify RUNNER is mechanism; the
# repo's gate list is the .harness/gates.conf policy file below.)
